Class Reactive

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.windowing.Scheme

        • com.yahoo.bullet.windowing.SlidingRecord
          • com.yahoo.bullet.windowing.Reactive
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closable, Initializable, Monoidal

    public class Reactive
extends SlidingRecord
    This window is just a SlidingRecord window with a maximum of one record - both SlidingRecord.isClosedForPartition() and SlidingRecord.isClosed() are identical. Using this will make results be emitted as they arrive - making it snappy or reactive.
